The controversial actress, Nkechi Blessing Sunday, has fired back at a popular controversial human rights activist, Reno Omokri after he used her as a reference to Tinubu. She has told him to remove her name from his mouth and the mix.
According to Nkechi Blessing Sunday, she has reacted angrily to one post Reno made and has told Reno never to try it again. She said, support Atiku all you want, but leave my name from that mix, I’m not a politician.
